2
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:10,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau...</font>

3
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:14,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...nyawa seluruh rakyat Joseon...</font>

4
00:00:14,890 --> 00:00:16,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah tanggung jawabmu.</font>

5
00:00:22,930 --> 00:00:24,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang Guru...</font>

6
00:00:26,590 --> 00:00:29,830
<font color=#FFFF00>..coba katakan, aku mengerti.</font>

7
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:33,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun,</font>

8
00:00:34,660 --> 00:00:36,300
<font color=#FFFF00>aku harus pergi.</font>

9
00:00:37,330 --> 00:00:40,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila demi menyelamatkan diri sendiri,
aku meninggalkan Ga Eun,</font>

10
00:00:42,330 --> 00:00:43,490
<font color=#FFFF00>maka aku pun...</font>

11
00:00:45,990 --> 00:00:48,190
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak akan sama lagi.</font>

12
00:00:48,190 --> 00:00:49,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, Jeoha...</font>

13
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:53,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang pria yang tidak bisa melindungi gadis tercintanya,</font>

14
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:55,990
<font color=#FFFF00>lalu rakyat Joseon ini akan dilindunginya...</font>

15
00:00:57,060 --> 00:00:58,730
<font color=#FFFF00>...seperti apa?</font>

16
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Tadinya aku ragu,</font>

17
00:01:54,990 --> 00:01:57,060
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi demi menyelamatkanmu, dia datang.</font>

18
00:02:16,790 --> 00:02:19,900
<font color=#FFFF00>Sarungkan pedangmu dan sambut tamu kita.</font>

19
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:33,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Berkali-kali aku gagal menemukan dan membunuhmu.</font>

20
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:37,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa demi seorang wanita kau suka rela menunjukkan diri?</font>

21
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:40,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sengaja menculik gadis ini untuk memancingku.</font>

22
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:44,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan Dae Mok yang aku kenal.</font>

23
00:02:44,460 --> 00:02:46,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku datang sesuai harapanmu.</font>

24
00:02:47,130 --> 00:02:49,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Maka lepaskan anak ini.</font>

25
00:02:51,230 --> 00:02:54,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akui, kau memang punya nyali.</font>

26
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:56,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurung dia di tempat semula.</font>

27
00:02:56,690 --> 00:02:58,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

28
00:02:59,790 --> 00:03:02,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan aku! Jangan sentuh aku!</font>

29
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:08,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Perlakukan dia dengan sopan.</font>

30
00:03:08,990 --> 00:03:11,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian tidak berhak memperlakukan dia dengan kasar.</font>

31
00:03:37,530 --> 00:03:39,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok menculik Ga Eun Aghassi?</font>

32
00:03:39,990 --> 00:03:41,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, itu benar.</font>

33
00:03:41,730 --> 00:03:43,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Ke--kenapa dia melakukannya?</font>

34
00:03:43,990 --> 00:03:45,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Hamba rasa...</font>

35
00:03:45,490 --> 00:03:48,560
<font color=#FFFF00>...Aghassi dijadikan umpan menangkap Seja asli.</font>

36
00:03:48,690 --> 00:03:52,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat mendengar Seja berhasil kabur dari Gerbang Shinmumun,</font>

37
00:03:52,330 --> 00:03:54,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok marah besar.</font>

38
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:56,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah...</font>

39
00:03:57,290 --> 00:03:59,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...bila Dae Mok menyingkirkan Seja asli...</font>

40
00:04:00,330 --> 00:04:02,530
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan lebih baik bagi Cheonha?</font>

41
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawakan baju safariku!</font>

42
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:08,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok belum menyakiti Ga Eun Aghassi.
Anda harus menunggu...</font>

43
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok... meski sedetik saja tidak boleh...</font>

44
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,990
<font color=#FFFF00>...bersama Ga Eun Aghassi.</font>

45
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:14,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus lekas pergi dan menyelamatkan Ga Eun Aghassi.</font>

46
00:04:27,630 --> 00:04:29,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin menjadi bunga seperti apa?</font>

47
00:04:34,990 --> 00:04:36,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terus berada di luar...</font>

48
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:39,360
<font color=#FFFF00>...baik saat ada badai maupun salju selama bertahun-tahun.</font>

49
00:04:39,590 --> 00:04:41,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Belum tiba waktunya kau mekar?</font>

50
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:48,230
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bunga ini tidak bisa mekar karena terus berada di dalam rumah hijau.</i></font>

51
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:50,660
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bukankah ini sangat menarik?</i></font>

52
00:04:51,330 --> 00:04:56,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bunga yang mekar usai diterpa badai maupun salju...</i></font>

53
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:58,960
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...adalah bunga sesungguhnya.</i></font>

54
00:05:05,930 --> 00:05:07,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Bungaku...</font>

55
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:11,430
<font color=#FFFF00>...saat Dae Mok dan Pyunsoo-hwe lenyap dari Joseon,</font>

56
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,160
<font color=#FFFF00>baru akan mekar.</font>

57
00:05:16,530 --> 00:05:20,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Tanpa aku, Dae Mok, dan juga Pyunsoo-hwe, Joseon akan...</font>

58
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:23,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa sebenarnya yang ingin...</font>

59
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:26,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau raih dengan menjatuhkan aku?</font>

60
00:05:26,490 --> 00:05:28,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Kekuatan absolut mengontrol pemerintahan?</font>

61
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:30,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Popularitas sepanjang masa?</font>

62
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau bukan,</font>

63
00:05:35,190 --> 00:05:36,260
<font color=#FFFF00>apakah...</font>

64
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:39,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...dendam orang tuamu?</font>

65
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:42,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan melenyapkan Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

66
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:45,660
<font color=#FFFF00>dan membawa era baru.</font>

67
00:05:45,660 --> 00:05:47,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Era baru?</font>

68
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:54,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita memiliki tujuan akhir yang sama.</font>

69
00:05:56,730 --> 00:05:58,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagimu, Joseon itu apa?</font>

70
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagiku, Joseon...</font>

71
00:06:03,290 --> 00:06:05,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah negeri menyedihkan.</font>

72
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka yang menikmati kenyamanan,
hanya Raja...</font>

73
00:06:06,930 --> 00:06:09,360
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan para bangsawan itu.</font>

74
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:12,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Sisanya miskin.</font>

75
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:16,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Negara seperti itu tidaklah baik.</font>

76
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:18,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika terus seperti ini,</font>

77
00:06:20,030 --> 00:06:22,590
<font color=#FFFF00>berapa lama Joseon akan bertahan?</font>

78
00:06:22,590 --> 00:06:26,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir berapa banyak mereka yang dilanda kemiskinan dapat bertahan?</font>

79
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Maukah kau bergabung denganku...</font>

80
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:36,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menjadi Raja Joseon yang bijak,</font>

81
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:38,790
<font color=#FFFF00>demi terciptanya negeri adidaya?</font>

82
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:48,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Negeri adidaya?</font>

83
00:06:53,690 --> 00:06:55,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Tujuan yang baru kau katakan tadi...</font>

84
00:06:56,930 --> 00:06:58,630
<font color=#FFFF00>...sama seperti keinginanku.</font>

85
00:07:00,530 --> 00:07:02,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, masalahnya adalah...</font>

86
00:07:02,090 --> 00:07:04,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...baik proses maupun hasilnya...</font>

87
00:07:04,890 --> 00:07:07,790
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau sama sekali tidak mau bertanggung-jawab.</font>

88
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Demi bisa mewujudkan Joseon-mu,</font>

89
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:14,430
<font color=#FFFF00>entah berapa anak yang sudah tewas.</font>

90
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:17,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Demi mendapatkan kekayaan pribadimu,
entah berapa orang yang telah mati.</font>

91
00:07:19,530 --> 00:07:21,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, kau hanya duduk dan menonton.</font>

92
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:26,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau, selama ini, tidak mau bertanggung-jawab.</font>

93
00:07:26,330 --> 00:07:30,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Kekuatan yang tidak bertanggung-jawab
lebih mengerikan dibanding perang.</font>

94
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:33,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Selama kau masih sibuk memanipulasi orang lain,</font>

95
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:39,030
<font color=#FFFF00>selama itu pula kau tidak layak bicara tentang era baru negeri ini.</font>

96
00:07:40,330 --> 00:07:41,530
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kebenaran?"</font>

97
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:45,060
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kebenaran?"</font>

98
00:07:45,860 --> 00:07:48,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibir seseorang yang hanya beruntung lahir di keluarga kerajaan,</font>

99
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,860
<font color=#FFFF00>tidak aku sangka dapat berkata begitu.</font>

100
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sendirilah...</font>

101
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:54,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang tidak memiliki hak menjadi Raja,</font>

102
00:07:54,290 --> 00:07:56,730
<font color=#FFFF00>atau bicara tentang era baru.</font>

103
00:07:58,690 --> 00:07:59,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu itu?</font>

104
00:08:05,590 --> 00:08:07,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sungguh tidak tahu apa-apa?</font>

105
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Mendiang ayahmu itu dan aku,</font>

106
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,130
<font color=#FFFF00>pernah menjadi rekan.</font>

107
00:08:21,130 --> 00:08:22,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bergabung denganku...</font>

108
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:26,260
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menghabisi Raja saat itu.</font>

109
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:34,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar.</font>

110
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:38,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menghabisi Raja saat itu..</font>

111
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:41,990
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menjadikan mendiang ayahmu sebagai Raja.</font>

112
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:45,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, kemudian ayahmu menipu...</font>

113
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan juga menjauh dariku.</font>

114
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:50,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, sekarang katakan padaku.</font>

115
00:08:50,930 --> 00:08:53,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang berhak dan tidak?</font>

116
00:08:53,530 --> 00:08:55,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapakah pengkhianat sesungguhnya?</font>

117
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:58,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang harus membalas dendam pada siapa?</font>

118
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:03,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok!
Aku tidak percaya ucapanmu sedikitpun!</font>

119
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:05,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Membunuh Raja yang bertakhta saat itu?</font>

120
00:09:06,490 --> 00:09:08,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Abamama tidak akan pernah mela--</font>

121
00:09:08,330 --> 00:09:10,060
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau mirip dengan dia.</i></font>

122
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,300
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau jelas terlihat...</i></font>

123
00:09:12,660 --> 00:09:17,530
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...seperti pengkhianat yang mencuri takhta Raja itu.</i></font>

124
00:09:41,990 --> 00:09:45,300
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Berkali-kali aku gagal menemukan dan membunuhmu.</i></font>

125
00:09:45,390 --> 00:09:48,530
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Namun, demi seorang gadis kau datang secara suka rela?</i></font>

126
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:51,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sesuai keinginanmu, aku sudah datang,</i></font>

127
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:54,190
<font color=#FFFF00><i>jadi bebaskan anak ini.</i></font>

128
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:00,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia membunuh ayahku.</font>

129
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Entah dia mati atau tidak...</font>

130
00:10:04,990 --> 00:10:06,730
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak peduli.</font>

131
00:10:15,190 --> 00:10:18,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila ingin mengubah dunia, maka kau harus berkompromi.</font>

132
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Bergabunglah denganku.</font>

133
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:27,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau menikahi Hwa Gun dan bergabung denganku,</font>

134
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,760
<font color=#FFFF00>maka aku akan...</font>

135
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,930
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjadikanmu Raja.</font>

136
00:10:36,130 --> 00:10:37,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau lakukan,</font>

137
00:10:37,930 --> 00:10:42,630
<font color=#FFFF00>impian dan masa depanku akan menjadi milikmu.</font>

138
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tahu...</font>

139
00:10:52,190 --> 00:10:55,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...cara menangkap Serigala di wilayah utara ketika musim dingin tiba?</font>

140
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:02,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Pisau berlumur darah...</font>

141
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:06,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...ditempatkan di jalanan yang akan dilewatinya.</font>

142
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:08,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemudian, Serigala yang terpikat pada aroma darah itu,</font>

143
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:11,160
<font color=#FFFF00>mulai menjilati pisau berdarah tersebut.</font>

144
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Lidahnya kemudian mati rasa,</font>

145
00:11:13,630 --> 00:11:16,760
<font color=#FFFF00>namun ia terus menjilatinya tanpa merasakan lidahnya telah terpotong,</font>

146
00:11:18,530 --> 00:11:21,630
<font color=#FFFF00>sampai kemudian... mati.</font>

147
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah maksudmu...</font>

148
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:30,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...penawaranku adalah pisau berdarah itu?</font>

149
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:33,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kubiarkan tawaran manis itu membuatku mendapat kekuasaan,</font>

150
00:11:35,060 --> 00:11:36,460
<font color=#FFFF00>sudah jelas aku akan...</font>

151
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...berakhir seperti itu juga.</font>

152
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:45,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menolak menerima tawaranku?</font>

153
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:46,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang,</font>

154
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:49,690
<font color=#FFFF00>kau akan membunuhku?</font>

155
00:11:50,490 --> 00:11:51,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

156
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:55,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertama-tama, tepat di depan matamu,
Ga Eun,</font>

157
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,960
<font color=#FFFF00>anak itu, akan kubunuh duluan.</font>

158
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:05,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak iu akan merasakan kesakitan terburuk yang belum pernah
dirasakan sebelumnya oleh siapapun.</font>

159
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membunuhnya.</font>

160
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:09,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah itu, baru kubunuh kau.</font>

161
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak boleh, Harabeoji!</font>

162
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:17,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Daepyunsoo! Cepat kembali ke kamarmu!</font>

163
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:21,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji, kumohon ampuni Jeoha.</font>

164
00:12:23,190 --> 00:12:24,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau adalah Daepyunsoo!</font>

165
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan siapa dia?</font>

166
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir, dia siapa?</font>

167
00:12:30,490 --> 00:12:34,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia adalah putra mendiang Raja,
musuh besar Pyunsoo-hwe!</font>

168
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:37,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, aku masih mencoba membujuknya.</font>

169
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:41,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang ini, baik bergabung dengan Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

170
00:12:41,530 --> 00:12:44,790
<font color=#FFFF00>menjadi cucu-menantu serta Raja,</font>

171
00:12:46,060 --> 00:12:47,490
<font color=#FFFF00>ditolaknya mentah-mentah.</font>

172
00:12:51,730 --> 00:12:53,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus bagaimana lagi?</font>

173
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:57,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji.</font>

174
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:00,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji.</font>

175
00:13:16,260 --> 00:13:20,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, aku akan memberikannya satu kesempatan lagi.</font>

176
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:22,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau, cobalah membujuknya sendiri.</font>

177
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun bila tetap tidak berhasil,</font>

178
00:13:28,190 --> 00:13:32,430
<font color=#FFFF00>jangan lagi kau minta kakekmu ini mengampuni nyawanya.</font>

179
00:13:57,730 --> 00:13:58,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

180
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:03,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Joseon memiliki sejarah panjang dengan...</font>

181
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:05,760
<font color=#FFFF00>...Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

182
00:14:06,230 --> 00:14:10,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Mustahil untuk benar-benar melenyapkannya.</font>

183
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:17,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan mencoba menyingkirkan Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

184
00:14:17,130 --> 00:14:18,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebagai gantinya, rangkul mereka.</font>

185
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Dana dari Pyunsoo-hwe...</font>

186
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:26,190
<font color=#FFFF00>...bisa Jeoha gunakan sebagai pondasi,</font>

187
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:27,930
<font color=#FFFF00>lalu kekuasaan dan otoritas Pyunsoo-hwe...</font>

188
00:14:27,990 --> 00:14:29,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...dapat Jeoha gunakan untuk mengontrol Joseon.</font>

189
00:14:31,230 --> 00:14:32,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong lakukan itu.</font>

190
00:14:35,490 --> 00:14:36,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala Saudagar.</font>

191
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:38,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha, ambil aku...</font>

192
00:14:40,030 --> 00:14:41,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan rangkul Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

193
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:46,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan untuk Pyunsoo-hwe, namun diri Jeoha.</font>

194
00:14:47,060 --> 00:14:48,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon,</font>

195
00:14:50,590 --> 00:14:53,890
<font color=#FFFF00>bergabunglah dengan kakekku dan jadilah Raja.</font>

196
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:58,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan berada di sisi Jeoha dan setia membantu.</font>

197
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala Saudagar.</font>

198
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:07,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

199
00:15:09,530 --> 00:15:11,490
<font color=#FFFF00>...mencintai gadis lain.</font>

200
00:15:12,460 --> 00:15:13,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kumohon,</font>

201
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:15,990
<font color=#FFFF00>jangan...</font>

202
00:15:17,390 --> 00:15:19,260
<font color=#FFFF00>...berusaha keras untukku.</font>

203
00:15:23,060 --> 00:15:24,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

204
00:15:25,490 --> 00:15:26,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Menjadi Ratu...</font>

205
00:15:27,830 --> 00:15:31,160
<font color=#FFFF00>...maupun wanitamu, bukanlah tujuanku.</font>

206
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:36,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha bisa menjadikan perempuan manapun duduk di sampingmu.</font>

207
00:15:42,130 --> 00:15:46,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya perlu menjadi Dae Mok selanjutnya
dan memberikan Pyunsoo-hwe pada Jeoha.</font>

208
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:48,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebab itu, Jeoha hanya perlu...</font>

209
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:52,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengatakan menerimaku dan bergabung dengan kakekku,</font>

210
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:55,060
<font color=#FFFF00>cukup itu saja.</font>

211
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku,</font>

212
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:02,660
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi aku tidak bisa melakukannya.</font>

213
00:16:03,160 --> 00:16:05,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak meminta hati Jeoha.</font>

214
00:16:06,390 --> 00:16:08,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Cukup katakan kau akan melakukannya.</font>

215
00:16:09,860 --> 00:16:11,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau masih belum mengerti?</font>

216
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:15,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menyerahkan seluruh hatiku pada Jeoha.</font>

217
00:16:21,830 --> 00:16:23,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah sebabnya.</font>

218
00:16:24,060 --> 00:16:27,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mendapatkan ketulusan cintamu,</font>

219
00:16:29,230 --> 00:16:32,060
<font color=#FFFF00>maka aku tidak ingin membalasnya dengan memberi dusta.</font>

220
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:35,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji...</font>

221
00:16:37,860 --> 00:16:40,790
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa kau pikir akan mengampuni nyawamu?</font>

222
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:46,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun-ah.</font>

223
00:16:47,530 --> 00:16:51,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Daepyunsoo Eureushin,
Dae Mok Eureushin memberi kami perintah.</font>

224
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua karenamu!</font>

225
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:30,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau lakukan ini?</font>

226
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:33,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Demi menyelamatkanmu, Jeoha akan kehilangan nyawanya!</font>

227
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:37,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria itu... akan mati?</font>

228
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:38,960
<font color=#FFFF00>"Pria itu"?</font>

229
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:42,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha mempertaruhkan nyawanya demi dirimu
dan kau menyebutnya "pria itu"?</font>

230
00:17:43,860 --> 00:17:45,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Pria itu membunuh ayahku!</font>

231
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:49,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Entah dia mati atau tidak, aku tidak peduli.</font>

232
00:17:52,060 --> 00:17:55,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sungguh tidak tahu apa-apa, 'kan?</font>

233
00:17:56,690 --> 00:17:58,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Pikirkan, sanggupkah Jeoha...</font>

234
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:00,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang tidak aku ketahui?</font>

235
00:18:01,330 --> 00:18:04,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha telah membunuh ayahmu?</font>

236
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:09,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.
Berpikir saja seperti itu dan benci Jeoha seumur hidupmu.</font>

237
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:12,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu itu?</font>

238
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:15,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau yang membunuh ayahku bukan Jeoha,</font>

239
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:18,230
<font color=#FFFF00>lalu siapa?</font>

240
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:27,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha.</font>

241
00:18:30,530 --> 00:18:32,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau yang membunuh ayahku...</font>

242
00:18:33,930 --> 00:18:35,530
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan kau, lantas siapa?</font>

243
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa membujuknya, 'kan?</font>

244
00:18:44,930 --> 00:18:45,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji.</font>

245
00:18:46,360 --> 00:18:48,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kumohon izinkan Seja Jeoha hidup.</font>

246
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:53,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau dia mau mengikuti ritual,
kubiarkan dia hidup.</font>

247
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:59,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Persiapkan ritual untuk Seja.</font>

248
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:00,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik, Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

249
00:19:01,390 --> 00:19:02,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Harabeoji.</font>

250
00:19:03,460 --> 00:19:04,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kalau Jeoha...</font>

251
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:07,560
<font color=#FFFF00>...menolak menjalani ritual?</font>

252
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:11,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, dia harus dibunuh.</font>

253
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:18,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Hwa Gun-ah, kakekmu...</font>

254
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:21,630
<font color=#FFFF00>...hanya berusaha memberikan yang terbaik untukmu.</font>

255
00:19:23,690 --> 00:19:24,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan kuatir.</font>

256
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:27,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu ini punya rencana.</font>

257
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Sesudah menjalani ritual,</font>

258
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:36,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja pun akan menjadi bagian dari Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

259
00:19:39,230 --> 00:19:42,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu ini akan menyembuhkan ketergantungannya kemudian.</font>

260
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun,</font>

261
00:19:45,730 --> 00:19:48,130
<font color=#FFFF00>penawarnya hanya Harabeoji yang tahu.</font>

262
00:19:49,690 --> 00:19:52,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir selama menjadi Daepyunsoo...</font>

263
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:54,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku hanya membuang-buang waktuku?</font>

264
00:19:57,930 --> 00:19:59,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Percayalah pada ayahmu ini?</font>

265
00:20:06,060 --> 00:20:09,060
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kaulah yang tidak memiliki hak menjadi Raja.</i></font>

266
00:20:09,060 --> 00:20:11,390
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau pun tidak layak bicara tentang era baru.</i></font>

267
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:13,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mendiang ayahmu dan aku...</i></font>

268
00:20:14,290 --> 00:20:15,590
<font color=#FFFF00><i>..sempat menjadi rekan.</i></font>

269
00:20:15,830 --> 00:20:17,160
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia bergabung denganku...</i></font>

270
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:20,830
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan membunuh Raja saat itu.</i></font>

271
00:20:26,730 --> 00:20:28,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Abamama.</font>

272
00:20:54,430 --> 00:20:55,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya hendak menjemput Anda.</font>

273
00:20:56,730 --> 00:20:57,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa...</font>

274
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan menyelamatkan Jeoha, malah menjemputku?</font>

275
00:21:01,260 --> 00:21:04,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha menyuruh untuk menyelamatkan Aghassi.</font>

276
00:21:06,260 --> 00:21:08,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aghassi, kita tidak punya banyak waktu.</font>

277
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:25,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari pergi.</font>

278
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa pergi sendirian.</font>

279
00:21:29,130 --> 00:21:30,790
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aghassi!
- Jeoha...</font>

280
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:33,830
<font color=#FFFF00>...harus menjelaskan kebenarannya padaku.</font>

281
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:36,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru, aku punya...</font>

282
00:21:36,660 --> 00:21:39,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...permintaan sulit padamu.</font>

283
00:21:40,190 --> 00:21:41,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekalipun aku menemui Dae Mok,</font>

284
00:21:42,230 --> 00:21:43,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok...</font>

285
00:21:44,260 --> 00:21:46,500
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak akan melepaskan Ga Eun dengan mudah.</font>

286
00:21:47,230 --> 00:21:48,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun...</font>

287
00:21:49,060 --> 00:21:51,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...adalah umpan untuk memancingku,</font>

288
00:21:51,990 --> 00:21:57,230
<font color=#FFFF00>namun dia juga alat untuk mengontrol Lee Sun.</font>

289
00:21:57,460 --> 00:21:59,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu, kenapa?</font>

290
00:22:01,890 --> 00:22:02,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru.</font>

291
00:22:03,860 --> 00:22:04,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

292
00:22:05,930 --> 00:22:09,360
<font color=#FFFF00>...mungkin tidak akan selamat dari Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

293
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:12,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, Ga Eun tidak boleh begitu.</font>

294
00:22:12,460 --> 00:22:13,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah mendapatkanku,</font>

295
00:22:14,030 --> 00:22:16,960
<font color=#FFFF00>pengawasan mereka terhadap Ga Eun akan berkurang,
saat itulah...</font>

296
00:22:17,990 --> 00:22:19,160
<font color=#FFFF00>...tolong selamatkan Ga Eun.</font>

297
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,630
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeoha.
- Kumohon.</font>

298
00:22:22,890 --> 00:22:23,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru.</font>

299
00:22:28,390 --> 00:22:30,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah Aghassi sampai di tempat yang aman,</font>

300
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:32,230
<font color=#FFFF00>saya akan menyelamatkan Jeoha.</font>

301
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:34,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, Aghassi harus meloloskan diri dulu.</font>

302
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:36,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya pertanyaan,</font>

303
00:22:37,530 --> 00:22:38,590
<font color=#FFFF00>tolong jawablah.</font>

304
00:22:42,330 --> 00:22:43,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahku...</font>

305
00:22:45,660 --> 00:22:46,890
<font color=#FFFF00>...siapa yang membunuhnya?</font>

306
00:23:04,530 --> 00:23:06,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Gyu Ho Eureushin dieksekusi oleh...</font>

307
00:23:09,730 --> 00:23:10,790
<font color=#FFFF00>...saya.</font>

308
00:23:14,530 --> 00:23:16,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya memakai topeng Jeoha.</font>

309
00:23:20,490 --> 00:23:22,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya yang mengeksekusi beliau.</font>

310
00:23:25,330 --> 00:23:26,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau?</font>

311
00:23:28,790 --> 00:23:30,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Membunuh ayahku?</font>

312
00:23:30,730 --> 00:23:34,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha sudah berusaha semaksimal mungkin menyelamatkan beliau.</font>

313
00:23:35,630 --> 00:23:37,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Semestinya, saya mengatakannya lebih awal.</font>

314
00:23:38,490 --> 00:23:40,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun, Jeoha melarang saya.</font>

315
00:23:41,530 --> 00:23:43,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Terlalu lama bagi saya untuk bisa meminta maaf.</font>

316
00:23:47,990 --> 00:23:49,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan saya.</font>

317
00:23:53,890 --> 00:23:55,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

318
00:23:55,760 --> 00:23:58,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Ke... kenapa Anda membawa Dayang Han?</font>

319
00:24:02,430 --> 00:24:04,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pun yang Eureushin kehendaki, akan saya kerjakan.</font>

320
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:06,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong kembalikan dia kepada saya.</font>

321
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:08,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terlambat.</font>

322
00:24:08,390 --> 00:24:10,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja sudah datang menyelamatkan dia.</font>

323
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:13,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat aku melepaskan anak itu,</font>

324
00:24:13,730 --> 00:24:15,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja bersedia menjalani ritual...</font>

325
00:24:16,930 --> 00:24:19,860
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan bergabung dengan Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

326
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:22,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila Seja bergabung dengan Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

327
00:24:22,990 --> 00:24:24,890
<font color=#FFFF00>lalu apa yang selanjutnya terjadi?</font>

328
00:24:24,890 --> 00:24:25,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Entahlah.</font>

329
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:30,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak akan memakai topeng itu lagi.</font>

330
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:34,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkinkah...</font>

331
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:36,930
<font color=#FFFF00>...saya akan dilengserkan...</font>

332
00:24:38,230 --> 00:24:40,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan Seja menaiki takhta?</font>

333
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:46,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Eureushin, saya selalu setia kepada Anda.</font>

334
00:24:47,290 --> 00:24:49,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa Anda melengserkan saya?</font>

335
00:24:49,230 --> 00:24:52,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Masalahnya, cucuku menyukai Seja.</font>

336
00:24:54,730 --> 00:24:57,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau Seja menikah dengan cucuku,</font>

337
00:25:00,290 --> 00:25:02,860
<font color=#FFFF00>maka bukan ide buruk mengembalikan takhtanya.</font>

338
00:25:13,230 --> 00:25:15,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok Eureushin ingin bertemu Anda.</font>

339
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:26,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja palsu...</font>

340
00:25:26,630 --> 00:25:28,690
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengatakan dia akan setia pada Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

341
00:25:28,690 --> 00:25:30,560
<font color=#FFFF00>asal aku melepaskan gadis itu.</font>

342
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah sekarang, Raja palsu ini...</font>

343
00:25:41,730 --> 00:25:43,590
<font color=#FFFF00>...kubiarkan saja membawa pergi gadis itu?</font>

344
00:25:47,730 --> 00:25:49,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak menjawab?</font>

345
00:25:50,230 --> 00:25:52,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak ingin menyelamatkan Aghassi?</font>

346
00:25:55,930 --> 00:25:57,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah keselamatan Aghassi tidak jadi soal buatmu?</font>

347
00:25:58,290 --> 00:26:00,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak ingin Aghassi pergi bersamaku?</font>

348
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:04,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Lee Sun-ah.</font>

349
00:26:06,230 --> 00:26:08,630
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ga Eun...
- Dia mungkin sudah kabur.</font>

350
00:26:20,730 --> 00:26:23,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu, tidak peduli seberapa gesit dirimu,</font>

351
00:26:23,490 --> 00:26:25,460
<font color=#FFFF00>kau tidak akan bisa lolos dari Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

352
00:26:37,760 --> 00:26:39,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru! Guru!</font>

353
00:26:40,430 --> 00:26:41,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan hamba,</font>

354
00:26:42,460 --> 00:26:43,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

355
00:26:45,730 --> 00:26:47,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sudah mengurungnya lagi.</font>

356
00:26:49,130 --> 00:26:51,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Selagi kau mengulur waktu,</font>

357
00:26:52,630 --> 00:26:55,490
<font color=#FFFF00>orangmu akan menyelamatkan gadis itu?</font>

358
00:26:56,560 --> 00:26:59,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir... kau bisa membodohiku?</font>

359
00:27:07,530 --> 00:27:08,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Guru!!!</font>

360
00:27:11,690 --> 00:27:13,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok!</font>

361
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:17,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Semakin lama kau ragu-ragu,</font>

362
00:27:18,730 --> 00:27:21,360
<font color=#FFFF00>kau akan kehilangan abdi setiamu.</font>

363
00:27:27,690 --> 00:27:29,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

